# Data Structures

## Product (object)
+ id: '0123456789'
+ name: 'Champions T-Shirt'
+ price: 12.99
+ currency: 'USD'
+ childSKUs: ['0123456789', '0123456780']
+ category: 'clothing'

## SKU (object)
+ id: '0123456789'
+ size: 'M'
+ productId: '0123456789'

# Tax Rule
+ category: 'clothing'
+ tax: 0.12

## State Rules (object)
+ id: '0123456789'
+ state: 'PA'
+ rules: []

## Commerce Item
+ skuId: '0123456789'
+ quantity: 2

